title: Dermablend Loose Setting Powder Original, 1 Ounce
description: Keep perfection lasting longer with Dermablend Loose Setting Powder - Original. Ensures smudge-resistance and enhances the wearability of dermablend coverage products for up to 16 hours of wear. Transparent upon application and fragrance free.

title: Burt's Bees Radiance Eye Cream, 0.5 Ounces
description: How to determine the expiration date:The lot code is six to seven digits long and starts with a 0, 1, 2 or 3. To read the lot code, the first three numbers are the day of the year the product was made (aka Julian Date). The next two digits are the year, and the last two digits are a batch number we use internally for identification. For example, lot code 0400901 translates to a product made on February 9, 2009 from Batch Number 1.

title: BASQNYC Cucumber Tea Eye Gel, 0.5oz
description: Give your eyes a fresh start with Basq's soothing cooling Cucumber Tea Eye Gel. This antioxidant rich blend with Cucumber and Green Tea helps soothe eye puffiness and smooth fine lines while rich hydrators and a gentle cooling tingle awaken eye area. For daily use, just dab under the eye area or for a more intense treatment at night smooth on a thicker layer before sleep.
